    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - FULLER 10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS - INSPECT - BEARINGS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>BEARINGS</title>
        <para>Inspect balls, rollers, races, and thrust surfaces for pitting, spalling, or discoloration. Check for
            excessive axial (up and down) or radial (side-to-side) play. Replace the bearings as necessary.
        </para>
        <para>Lubricate bearings with clean oil and rotate them, checking for tightness or roughness. Replace the
            bearings as necessary.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
